pport.%20And%20in%20nations%20where%20the%20military%20is%20focused%20more%20on%20crushing%20internal%20opposition%20than%20defeating%20foreign%20invaders%2C%20an%20armored%20car%20is%20as%20good%20as%20a%20tank%20when%20it%20comes%20intimidating%20protestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20has%20brought%20new%20attention%20to%20the%20value%20of%20wheeled%20armor%20in%20a%20mechanized%20war%20waged%20by%20traditional%20heavy%20weapons%20such%20as%20tanks%2C%20artillery%2C%20and%20guided%20missiles.%20Ukrainian%20forces%20in%20particular%20is%20using%20a%20variety%20of%20wheeled%20vehicles%2C%20including%20French%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrance-is-sending-tank-killing-amx10rc-armored-vehicles-to-ukraine-2023-1%5C%22%3EAMX-10RC%20heavy%20armored%20cars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20US%20Stryker%20infantry%20fighting%20vehicles%2C%20and%20French%20Caesar%20155-mm%20self-propelled%20artillery.%20Both%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%20also%20have%20a%20variety%20of%20Soviet-era%20wheeled%20vehicles%2C%20such%20as%20BTR%20troop%20carriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWheeled%20vehicles%20are%20lighter%3A%20An%20AMX-10RC%20weighs%2016%20tons%20and%20a%20Stryker%20about%2020%20tons%2C%20compared%20to%2070%20tons%20for%20the%20latest%20M1A2%20Abrams.%20Modern%20wheeled%20armor%20can%20also%20be%20quite%20sophisticated%2C%20capable%20of%20carrying%20heavy%20cannon%2C%20anti-tank%20missiles%2C%20and%20big%20howitzers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20active-protection%20systems%20to%20intercept%20anti-tank%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221776%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22French%20soldiers%20in%20an%20AMX-10RC%20in%20Afghanistan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c96ab0eee94d001a78f186%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrench%20soldiers%20practice%20shooting%20an%20AMX-10RC%20in%20Afghanistan%20on%202010.%3Cp%3EJOEL%20SAGET%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20there%20is%20a%20good%20reason%20for%20tanks%20and%20many%20troop%20carriers%20to%20be%20tracked.%20They%20can%20carry%20heavier%20armament%20and%20armor%20protection%2C%20and%20tracks%20offer%20superior%20off-road%20maneuverability%20in%20terrain%20that%20would%20damage%20or%20bog%20down%20wheeled%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETires%20are%20also%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20damage%20than%20tracks%2C%20as%20Ukrainian%20troops%20have%20discovered.%20The%20%26quot%3Bweakness%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20AMX-10RC%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20wheels%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Ukrainian%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.defence-ua.com%2Fevents%2Fukrainian_soldiers_describe_first_amx_10rc_combat_once_again_about_why_its_not_a_tank-7383.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20using%20the%20vehicle%20in%20combat%20this%20summer.%20%26quot%3BFragmentation%20cuts%20up%20all%20the%20wheels%20in%20an%20instant.%20It%20impacts%20the%20speed%2C%20the%20maneuverability%2C%20all%20the%20advantages%20of%20this%20tank%20are%20instantly%20gone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20suggests%20that%20while%20wheels%20might%20be%20fine%20on%20roads%20or%20on%20firm%20or%20sandy%20soil%2C%20tracks%20can%20perform%20better%20on%20soft%2C%20wet%20soils.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPut%20simply%2C%20the%20argument%20that%20wheeled%20vehicles%20can%20match%20the%20off-road%20mobility%20of%20tracked%20vehicles%20does%20not%20have%20a%20wheel%20to%20stand%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Sam%20Cranny-Evans%2C%20a%20British%20defense%20and%20land-warfare%20analyst%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuro-sd.com%2F2023%2F01%2Farticles%2F29120%2Fthe-role-of-wheeled-vehicles-in-peer-conflict-and-the-tracks-vs-wheels-debate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year.%20%26quot%3BA%20force%20that%20structures%20its%20procurements%20primarily%20around%20wheeled%20vehicles%20and%20finds%20itself%20unable%20to%20move%20over%20the%20terrain%20it%20is%20defending%20will%20likely%20be%20punished%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukraine%20BTR-4E%20wheeled%20armored%20personnel%20carriers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578b4f00ec98e92f74ea5ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20troops%20train%20on%20BTR-4E%20wheeled%20armored%20personnel%20carriers%20in%20the%20Kharkiv%20region%20in%20April.%3Cp%3ESERGEY%20BOBOK%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201990s%2C%20studies%20suggested%20that%20wheels%20are%20better%20for%20carrying%20light%20loads%20for%20long%20distances%20over%20roads%2C%20Cranny-Evans%20noted.%20For%20vehicles%20over%2050%20tons%2C%20tracks%20were%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20between%20wheeled%20or%20tracked%20vehicles%20all%20comes%20down%20to%20terrain%2C%20according%20to%20Cranny-Evans.%20Under%20the%20right%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20with%20good%20roads%20or%20on%20firm%20soil%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wheeled%20vehicle%20might%20be%20armed%20and%20armored%20to%20the%20level%20of%20a%20tank.%20But%20on%20wet%20terrain%2C%20that%20vehicle%20is%20a%20sitting%20duck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20troops%20in%20combat%20will%20take%20their%20wheeled%20and%20tracked%20vehicles%20%26quot%3Bwherever%20they%20feel%20they%20need%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Cranny-Evans%20wrote%2C%20which%20makes%20training%20and%20instruction%20vital%20for%20both%20the%20troops%20in%20the%20vehicles%20and%20the%20strategists%20deciding%20how%20to%20employ%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdequately%20informing%20them%20of%20the%20limits%20of%20their%20vehicles%2C%20from%20the%20driver%20to%20the%20officers%20leading%20operations%20and%20planning%20routes%2C%20will%20help%20them%20avoid%20committing%20to%20scenarios%20that%20the%20technology%20cannot%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20Cranny-Evans%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20a%20master's%20in%20political%20science.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22a48008f66dd60e4ae3cb2319a8aa10eb%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20data-xid%3D%5C%22fr1661352660482ifa%5C%22%20data-ml-dynamic-type%3D%5C%22sl%5C%22%20data-ml%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-skimlinks-tracking%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-am-orig-url%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D031b2d50cbdac0fa31e91243bf4d02324deef0918da59c6d06089ce83c069930%26amp%3Bu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fin%252Fmipeck%252F%5C%22%20data-ml-dynamic%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20data-orig-url%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-ml-id%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22b272b0682b12cef8f32e027c89f10c0f%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-showing-value-and-weakness-of-wheeled-armored-vehicles-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%