d%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20plum%20routes%20might%20include%20a%20neighborhood%20without%20a%20lot%20of%20hills%20%E2%80%94%20or%20neighborhoods%20with%20houses%20instead%20of%20apartment%20buildings%20that%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E5.%20Seniority%20matters%20at%20UPS%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20of%20the%20delivery%20drivers%20at%20UPS%20have%20been%20with%20the%20company%20for%2010%20years%20or%20more%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosato%20started%20at%20the%20company%20in%201989%2C%20and%20she%20has%20colleagues%20who%20are%20more%20senior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20UPS%20truck%20makes%20its%20way%20down%20a%20snowy%20street%20during%20a%20winter%20storm.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cc4297a3c8094d5ddbfe4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22691%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThrough%20all%20kinds%20of%20weather%3A%20UPS%20drivers%20have%20to%20make%20their%20way%20through%20snowstorms%20and%20worse%20as%20they%20deliver%20packages.%3Cp%3EMediaNews%20Group%2FDaily%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E6.%20It%20takes%2030%20days%20to%20prove%20yourself%20as%20a%20driver%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20of%20safety%20training%20and%20supervised%20drives%20are%20required%20before%20you%20can%20call%20yourself%20a%20full-fledged%20UPS%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20other%20training%20courses%2C%20Rosato%20said%20a%20supervisor%20will%20go%20out%20with%20you%20for%20three%20or%20four%20days%20of%20drives%2C%20but%20you'll%20then%20be%20expected%20to%20do%20a%20short%20route%20on%20your%20own%20once%20you%20get%20into%20the%20rhythm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E7.%20You'll%20be%20missed%20at%20home%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20can%20expect%20to%20work%208-%20to%2010-hour%20shifts%20that%20start%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20end%20in%20the%20evening.%20For%20new%20drivers%2C%20they%20can%20be%20called%20on%20at%20any%20time%20to%20cover%20a%20coworker's%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20to%20fit%20your%20life%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20Zambruno%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20ask%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20flexibility%20from%20the%20applicants%20that%20come%20in%20the%20door.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E8.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20lift%20more%20than%20the%20competition%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jobs-ups.com%2Fjob%2Fauburn%2Ffull-time-driver-dockworker%2F1187%2F57190672096%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20listings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20UPS%20asks%20candidates%20to%20be%20able%20to%20lift%20at%20least%2070%20pounds.%20Fellow%20delivery%20drivers%20at%20Amazon%20and%20FedEx%20are%20only%20expect%20to%20lift%2050%20pounds%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famazon-na.fountain.com%2Fapply%2Famazon-delivery-service-partner%2Fopening%2Fdelivery-associate-dew5-new-york-ny-starting-pay-17-00-hr%3Futm_campaign%3DAmazonDelivers.Jobs%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_source%3DAmazonDelivers.Jobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20job%20listings%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20both%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ups-drivers-earn-six-figure-salaries-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702817941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c65ec7a3c8094d5dd6d10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ups-drivers-earn-six-figure-salaries-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UPS%20veterans%20know%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20reach%20the%20%24170%2C000%20pay%20package%20their%20drivers%20receive.%20They%20told%20us%20all%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-up