-they-hid-for-decades-cxk9cqz5w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EItalian%20family%20has%20handed%20over%20a%20long-lost%20Botticelli%20%26quot%3BMadonna%20and%20Child%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20valued%20at%20%24109%20million%2C%20to%20Italian%20police%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20London%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnrico%20Somma%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmissing-botticelli-masterpiece-found-hanging-in-familys-home-2023-12%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20took%20custody%20of%20the%2015th-century%20Renaissance%20masterpiece%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%201960s%20when%20he%20removed%20it%20from%20a%20village%20chapel%20in%20southern%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20concerns%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20security%2C%20weary%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20art%20theft%20from%20Italian%20churches%20was%20common%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeppe%20Di%20Massa%2C%20a%20local%20historian%2C%20says%20that%20the%20painting%20was%20once%20owned%20by%20Pope%20Sixtus%20IV%2C%20who%20sold%20it%20to%20the%20Medici%20family%20in%20Florence%20to%20build%20the%20Vatican's%20Sistine%20Chapel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20eventually%20found%20its%20way%20to%20the%20chapel%20in%20Santa%20Maria%20La%20Carita%2C%20before%20being%20furtively%20acquired%20by%20the%20Sommas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Somma%20family%20insists%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bacting%20as%20custodians%26quot%3B%20and%20never%20wanted%20to%20make%20money%20off%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMichele%20Somma%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ereticent%20about%20the%20Botticelli's%20last%20hiding%20place%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20local%20rumors%2C%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20successful%20bakery%20business%20he%20owns%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20a%20village%20outside%20Naples%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20per%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20removal's%20legality%20remains%20unclear%2C%20scholars%20and%20art%20authorities%20acknowledged%20the%20painting's%20relocation%20in%20the%20late%201960s%2C%20listing%20it%20as%20a%20protected%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20artwork%2C%20painted%20in%20tempera%20on%20wood%2C%20portrays%20the%20Madonna%20holding%20Jesus%2C%20with%20art%20historians%20suggesting%20the%20model%20was%20Simonetta%20Vespucci%2C%20known%20for%20inspiring%20Botticelli's%20female%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnrico%2C%20always%20on%20guard%2C%20protected%20the%20painting%20from%20theft.%20He%20even%20kept%20a%20gun%20by%20his%20bedside.%20The%20family%20rebuffed%20numerous%20offers%20to%20buy%20the%20masterpiece%2C%20opting%20instead%20to%20hide%20it%20after%20Enrico's%20death%20to%20discourage%20interest%20and%20potential%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20rumors%20circulated%20and%20social%20media%20emerged%2C%20the%20family%20grew%20worried%20and%20decided%20to%20confess%20and%20return%20the%20artwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20painting%20had%20been%20kept%20by%20the%20Sommas%20in%20a%20village%20outside%20of%20Naples.%20The%20region%20is%20home%20to%20the%20criminal%20gangs%20of%20the%20Camorra%2C%20which%20also%20put%20the%20family%20and%20painting%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'The%20Madonna%20was%20like%20another%20mother%20to%20us'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22uffizi%20gallery%20florence%20shutterstock%20vvoe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a561573a75e2013048b4835%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Botticelli%20masterpiece%20is%20being%20restored%20at%20the%20Uffizi%20Gallery%20in%20Florence%2C.%3Cp%3EShutterstock%2Fvvoe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20painting%20was%20shrouded%20in%20secrecy%20and%20rife%20with%20rumors%20outside%20the%20household%20and%20within%20the%20family.%20The%20younger%20generations%20of%20Sommas%20were%20kept%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20artwork's%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20Sommas%20were%20neither%20told%20about%20nor%20shown%20the%20painting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E