2C161%20hours%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20JetSpy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20had%20a%20busy%20year%20after%20buying%20Twitter%20in%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20easy%20running%20six%20companies%2C%20but%20Elon%20Musk's%20fleet%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-who-tracks-elon-musk-private-jet-permanently-banned-twitter-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20jets%3C%2Fa%3E%20certainly%20helps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter-reach-agreement-to-close-acquisition-deal-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20over%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20(now%20X)%20late%20last%20year%2C%20Musk%20has%20been%20splitting%20his%20time%20between%20Texas%20and%20California%20%E2%80%94%20trading%20off%20sleeping%20on%20Tesla's%20factory%20floor%20for%20Twitter's%20offices%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20private%20jets%20have%20the%20mileage%20to%20show%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20private%20planes%20%E2%80%94%20worth%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%20at%20list%20value%20%E2%80%94%20took%20to%20the%20skies%20441%20times%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20data%20that%20was%20compiled%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjetspy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejet-tracking%20site%20JetSpy%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20of%20December%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20currently%20owns%20two%20Gulfstream%20private%20jets%3A%20a%20G650ER%2C%20registered%20N628TS%2C%20and%20a%20G550%2C%20registered%20N272BG%2C%20according%20to%20JetSpy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20second%20G550%20with%20the%20tail%20number%20N502SX%20was%20registered%20to%20SpaceX%20in%20September%202021%2C%20which%20has%20flown%20about%20630%20hours%20across%20246%20flights%20as%20of%20December%2014%2C%20per%20JetSpy%2C%20and%20could%20be%20used%20to%20fly%20company%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20purposes%20of%20this%20article%2C%20the%20second%20G550%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20billionaire's%20total%20flying%20because%20the%20jet%20is%20not%20registered%20to%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20two%20private%20planes%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-new-jet-gulfstream-g700-photos-tour-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Musk%20has%20also%20reportedly%20ordered%20the%20recently%20launched%20Gulfstream%20G700%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20at%20one%20time%20owned%20a%20Dassault%20Falcon%20900B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G650ER%2C%20which%20Musk%20acquired%20in%202016%2C%20is%20the%20longest-ranged%20plane%20of%20the%20collection%20and%20allows%20the%20billionaire%20to%20fly%20some%208%2C600%20miles%20nonstop.%20Gulfstream's%20larger%20jets%20like%20Musks'%20are%20typically%20fit%20with%20a%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224460%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk's%20private%20jet%20landed%20at%20an%20airport%20in%20Beijing%20in%20May.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64775c08085acb0018fefe16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222974%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk's%20G650ER%20private%20jet%20landed%20at%20an%20airport%20in%20Beijing%20in%20May.%3Cp%3ETingshu%20Wang%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20aircraft%20were%20in%20flight%20for%20more%20than%201%2C161%20hours%2C%20equivalent%20to%20over%2048%20days%20worth%20of%20time%20spent%20in%20the%20air%2C%20according%20to%20JetSpy%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJetSpy%20aggregates%20its%20flight%20information%20using%20ADS-B%20data%20that%20is%20transmitted%20from%20several%20vendors%20and%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-tracks-elon-musk-jet-calls-for-boycott-adsb-exhange-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EADS-B%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20public%20surveillance%20technology%20that%20broadcasts%20information%20like%20GPS%20location%20and%20altitude%20fr