ilar%20to%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20for%20a%20plane%20to%20fly%20from%20Hawthorne%20California%20(where%20SpaceX%20is%20headquartered)%20to%20Brownsville%2C%20Texas%20(SpaceX's%20launch%20site%20and%20the%20state%20where%20Musk%20moved%20Tesla's%20headquarters).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Musk's%20G650%2C%20the%20jet's%20most%20popular%20destinations%20are%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20airports%20in%20Oakland%20and%20San%20Jose%2C%20California.%20The%20private%20plane%20has%20taken%20166%20flights%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Musk's%20Gulfstream%20G550%20with%20the%20tail%20number%20N2727BG%20has%20taken%20275%20flights%20as%20of%20December%2014%2C%20according%20to%20JetSpy.%20The%20aircraft%20frequently%20visits%20airports%20in%20Hawthorne%20and%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20California%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Brownsville%20South%20Padre%20Island%20International%20Airport%20near%20SpaceX's%20launch%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Sweeney%2C%20who%20tracks%20Musk's%20private%20jets%2C%20has%20said%20the%20billionaire's%20habitual%20flight%20patterns%20can%20be%20a%20dead%20giveaway%20for%20identifying%20his%20planes%2C%20even%20as%20he%20has%20tried%20to%20obscure%20his%20flight%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221176%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk's%20private%20jet%20flight%20with%20PIA%20flag%2C%20tracked%20by%20Jack%20Sweeney.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653ad7f896f7540cd067330e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk's%20private%20jet%20flight%20with%20PIA%20flag%2C%20tracked%20by%20Jack%20Sweeney.%3Cp%3EJack%20Sweeney%20via%20ADS-B%20Exchange%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20longest%20flight%20one%20of%20Musk's%20jets%20took%20in%202023%20was%20a%20nearly%2013-hour%20flight%20to%20Tokyo%20in%20August.%20Musk%2C%20his%20on-and-off%20girlfriend%20Grimes%2C%20and%20their%20three-year-old%20son%20X%20were%20%3Ca%2