%20surplus%20cheese%2C%20dried%20beans%2C%20peanut%20butter%2C%20and%20dried%20milk).%20So%20an%20oversize%20magical%20elf%20was%20just%20as%20rational%20an%20explanation%20as%20any%20for%20the%20gifts%20piled%20beside%20our%20trailer's%20wood%20stove%20every%20Christmas%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20morning%2C%20there%20was%20nothing.%20Mom%20got%20up%20with%20a%20gasp%20and%20ran%20through%20the%20trailer%20like%20she%20had%20forgotten%20something%20and%20retrieved%20a%20stack%20of%20wrapped%20packages%20from%20somewhere%20outside%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20the%20naked%20underbelly%20of%20the%20trailer%2C%20maybe%20the%20cab%20of%20our%20beat-up%2C%20broken-down%20Dodge%20pickup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGratitude%20staved%20off%20any%20temptation%20to%20feel%20heartbroken%20or%20lied%20to.%20The%20provenance%20of%20the%20presents%20was%20still%20just%20as%20mysterious%20as%20Santa.%20The%20blinking%20light%20in%20the%20sky%20that%20night%20at%20the%20motel%20had%20been%20a%20plane%2C%20as%20I'd%20suspected.%20And%20there%20were%20bigger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbudgeting-holiday-shopping-throughout-year-avoid-debt-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissues%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20worry%20about%2C%20such%20as%20whether%20the%20roof%20would%20leak%2C%20or%20the%20pipes%20would%20freeze%2C%20or%20the%20sheets%20of%20polyester%20Mom%20stapled%20to%20the%20windows%20would%20keep%20out%20the%20draft%20through%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhile%20Christmas%20shopping%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20I%20discovered%20the%20truth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20I%20was%20out%20of%20college%2C%20a%20parent%20myself%20establishing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Forigins-of-common-christmas-traditions-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristmas%20traditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20my%20own%20little%20family%20and%20doing%20my%20middle-class%20shopping%20for%20toys%20my%20kids%20would%20forget%