ut%20that%20with%20no%20reforms%2C%20the%20UN%20is%20getting%20less%20and%20less%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20way%2C%20it's%20a%20human%20failing.%20But%20I%20think%20today%20it%20is%20harming%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20harming%20the%20world%20because%2C%20on%20key%20issues%20confronting%20the%20world%2C%20the%20UN%20is%20getting%20less%20and%20less%20effective%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20can%20also%20tell%20you%20the%20global%20sentiment.%20I%20mean%2C%20today%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20200%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%20do%20you%20want%20reform%20or%20don't%20you%20want%20reform%3F%20A%20very%20large%20number%20of%20countries%20would%20say%2C%20yes%2C%20we%20want%20reform...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20emphasising%20that%20nations%20are%20urging%20for%20reforms%20efforts%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20prevailing%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20September%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20resistance%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20reform%20its%20structure%2C%20will%20eventually%20lead%20to%20the%20body%20being%20%26quot%3Banachronistic%26quot%3B%20and%20people%20will%20start%20finding%20solutions%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20gave%20an%20%26quot%3Binjudicious%26quot%3B%20reference%20of%20passengers%20sitting%20in%20a%20bus%20drawing%20a%20comparison%20with%20the%20permanent%20members%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20somewhere%20injudiciously...described%20it%20like%20a%20passenger%20in%20a%20bus.%20A%20person%20sitting%20on%20the%20seat%2C%20will%20not%20vacate%20it%20for%20the%20next%20person.%20So%20there%20are%20these%20five%20guys%20sitting.%20Sometimes%2C%20you%20see%20such%20passengers%2C%20you%20see%20someone%20is%20tired%2C%20someone%20is%20carrying%20a%20baby%2C%20they%20will%20not%20get%20up%20and%20give%20up%20that%20seat%2C%