Cup%202023%2C%20where%20India%20were%20beaten%20by%20Australia%20in%20the%20final.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKS%20Bharat%20last%20featured%20for%20India%20in%20a%20Test%20back%20in%20June%20this%20year%20when%20the%20national%20team%20took%20on%20Australia%20in%20a%20Test%20series.%20Bharat%20had%20only%20made%20his%20Test%20debut%20for%20India%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20that%20too%20against%20Australia.%C2%A0Bharat%20wasn't%20the%20BCCI's%20plans%20for%20the%20Test%20assignment%20against%20South%20Africa%20but%20had%20to%20be%20brought%20in%20after%20Ishan's%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20release%2C%20the%20BCCI%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BMr%20Ishan%20Kishan%20has%20requested%20the%20BCCI%20to%20be%20released%20from%20the%20upcoming%20Test%20series%20against%20South%20Africa%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%20The%20wicket-keeper%20has%20subsequently%20been%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20Test%20squad.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Men's%20Selection%20Committee%20has%20named%20Mr%20KS%20Bharat%20as%20a%20replacement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20might%20not%20be%20the%20first-choice%20wicket-keeper%20for%20India%20in%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20South%20Africa%2C%20with%20reports%20emerging%20that%20KL%20Rahul%20could%20be%20tried%20for%20the%20spot%20behind%20the%20stumps.%20Rahul%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20handy%20option%20behind%20the%20stumps%20both%20in%20T20Is%20and%20ODIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Rishabh%20Pant%20still%20far%20from%20making%20a%20comeback%2C%20odds%20favour%20Rahul%20to%20be%20tried%20as%20a%20wicket-keeper%20across%20three%20formats.%20However%2C%20wicket-keeping%20in%20Tests%20remains%20a%20much%20difficult%20task%2C%20in%20comparison%20to%20ODIs%20and%20T20Is.%20It%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20the%20BCCI%20decides%20to%20manage%20Rahul's%20workload%20if%20he%20is%20made%20a%20full-time%20wicket-keeper%20in%20all%20three%20formats.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20squad%20fo