%20access%20to%20address%20urgent%20needs%20in%20north%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGaza%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWHO%20staff%20participated%20in%20a%20joint%20UN%20mission%20to%20Al-Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20north%20Gaza%20on%2016%20December%20to%20deliver%20health%20supplies%20and%20assess%20the%20situation%20in%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgIa3tG97mC%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FgIa3tG97mC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20(%40WHO)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWHO%2Fstatus%2F1736166107793301638%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20displaced%20people%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20the%20hospital%20building%20and%20grounds%2C%20and%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20shortage%26quot%3B%20of%20drinking%20water%20and%20food.%20The%20department%20had%20hundreds%20of%20patients%20and%20new%20ones%20kept%20arriving%20every%20minute.%20%26quot%3BPatients%20with%20trauma%20injuries%20were%20being%20sutured%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20no%20pain%20management%20is%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20said%20Al-Shifa%20is%20functioning%20at%20a%20minimal%20scale%20with%20very%20few%20staff.%20The%20situation%20isn't%20better%20at%20Al%20Awda%20and%20Al%20Sahaba%20Medical%20Complex%2C%20and%20Al-Ahli%20Arab%20is%20the%20only%20%26quot%3Bpartially%20functioning%26quot%3B%20hospital%20in%20entire%20north%20Gaza.%20The%20blockaded%20strip%20had%2024%20operational%20health%20facilities%20before%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20critical%20are%20being%20transferred%20to%20Al-Ahli%20Arab%20Hospital%20for%20surgeries%20as%20operation%20theatres%20are%20not%20working%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20oxygen%20and%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20most%20important%20and%20largest%20referral%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Al-Shifa%20now%20houses%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20doctors%20and%20a%20few%20nurses%2C%20together%20with%2070%20volunteers%2C%20working%20under%20what%20WHO%20staff%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bunbelievably%20challenging%20circumstances%26quot%3B%20and%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bhospital%20in%20need%20of%20resuscitation%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20WHO%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20only%2030%20patients%20at%20the%20hospital%20can%20receive%20dialysis%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20will%20be%20reinforced%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20so%20it%20can%20resume%20basic%20services%2C%20the%20WHO%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUp%20to%2020%20operating%20theatres%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20as%20well%20as%20post-operative%20care%20services%2C%20can%20be%20activated%20if%20provided%20with%20regular%20supplies%20of%20fuel%2C%20oxygen%2C%20medicines%2C%20food%2C%20and%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20bombardments%20have%20affected%20all%20health%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20Gaza%20strip%20with%20the%20country%20accusing%20the%20Palestinian%20Hamas%20group%20of%20running%20a%20command%20centre%20below%20the%20hospital.%20Officials%20at%20the%20hospital%20had%20denied%20such%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20counterattack%20began%20following%20Hamas's%20October%207's%20terror%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20territory%20that%20led%20to%201%2C140%20deaths%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20while%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20were%20taken%20across%20the%20Gaza%20border.%20The%20death%20count%20on%20Gaza%20side%20has%20crossed%2018%2C800%2C%20mostly%20comprising%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702805760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fuovsq8l_alshifa-hospital-december-10-afp_625x300_17_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-