was%20recorded%2C%20hosted%20the%209%2F11%20commission%20hearings.%20Former%20FBI%20director%20James%20Comey%20had%20also%20given%20his%20testimony%20on%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%20same%20room%20in%202017.%20The%20room%2C%20which%20carries%20significant%20historical%20distinction%2C%20also%20witnessed%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20justice%20Sonia%20Sotomayor%20becoming%20the%20first%20Latin%20American%20to%20attend%20nomination%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20the%20Capitol%20Police%20are%20looking%20into%20the%20matter.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnewsletters%2Fplaybook%2F2023%2F12%2F16%2Fsenate-staffer-out-after-sex-tape-scandal-00132143%5C%22%3E%20Politico%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Senator%20Ben%20Cardin's%20office%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAidan%20Maese-Czeropski%20is%20no%20longer%20employed%20by%20the%20US%20Senate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20fired%2C%20Aidan%20Maese-Czeropski%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20entire%20incident%20in%20a%20post%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Faidan-maese-czeropski-57147813b_this-has-been-a-difficult-time-for-me-as-activity-7141615313334276096-y4Bk%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%3ELinkedIn.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Mr%20Aidan%20did%20not%20address%20the%20video%20directly%20but%20said%20he%20was%20going%20through%20a%20difficult%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20detailed%20post%2C%20Aidan%20Maese-Czeropski%20also%20addressed%20an%20unrelated%20accusation%20that%20he%20accosted%20Congressman%20Max%20Miller%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20report%20added%20that%20Mr%20Miller%2C%20who%20is%20Jewish%2C%20was%20speaking%20to%20a%20journalist%20when%20a%20staffer%20allegedly%20confronted%20him%20to%20shout%20%E2%80%9CFree%20Palestine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%2C%20Aidan%20Maese-Czeropski%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20been%20a%20difficult%20time%20for%20me%2C%20as%20I%20have%20been%20attacked%20for%20who%20I%20love%20to%20pursue%20a%20political%20agenda.%20While%20some%20of%20my%20actions%20in%20the%20past%20have%20shown%20poor%20judgment%2C%20I%20love%20my%20job%20and%20would%20never%20disrespect%20my%20workplace.%20Any%20attempts%20to%20characterize%20my%20actions%20otherwise%20are%20fabricated%20and%20I%20will%20be%20exploring%20what%20legal%20options%20are%20available%20to%20me%20in%20these%20matters.%20As%20for%20the%20accusations%20regarding%20Congressman%20Max%20Miller%2C%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20the%20congressman%20and%20had%20no%20opportunity%20or%20cause%20to%20yell%20or%20confront%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Ben%20Cardin's%20office%20has%20reportedly%20released%20a%20statement%20that%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20media%20reports.%20As%20this%20is%20a%20personnel%20matter%20and%20under%20review%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20commenting%20further%20at%20this%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702805760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-06%2Fus-senate_650x400_41466083343.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsenate-staffer-loses-job-after-allegedly-having-sex-in-hearing-room-4690388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20The%20Guardian%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20men%20in%20the%20footage%20was%20widely%20named%20as%20Aidan%20Maese-Czeropski%2C%20a%20legislative%20aide%20for%20Senator%20Ben%20Cardin%20of%20Maryland%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsenate-staffer-loses-job-after-allegedly-having-sex-in-hearing-room-4690388%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsenate-staffer-loses-job-after-allegedly-having-sex-in-hearing-room-4690388%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt