lled-by-israeli-forces-in-west-banks-tulkarm-palestinian-health-ministry%2Farticleshow%2F106062282.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ffive-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-forces-in-west-banks-tulkarm-palestinian-health-ministry%2Famp_articleshow%2F106062282.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ffive-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-forces-in-west-banks-tulkarm-palestinian-health-ministry%2Famp_articleshow%2F106062282.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBecause%20Of%20This%26quot%3B%3A%20How%20Air%20Force's%20Ops%20Forced%20Pak%20To%20Surrender%20In%201971%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20celebrated%20Vijay%20Diwas%20yesterday%20to%20mark%20the%20surrender%20of%2093%2C000%20Pakistani%20troops%20and%20the%20liberation%20of%20Bangladesh.%20In%20a%20fortnight%20of%20fighting%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20opted%20for%20a%20truce%20over%20war%20following%20a%20well-coordinated%20three-pronged%20attack%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20Air%20Force%20and%20Navy%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Mukti%20Bahani%2C%20a%20guerilla%20force%20raised%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20officially%20began%20on%20December%203%2C%201971%2C%20and%20within%20three%20days%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20established%20air%20superiority%20in%20East%20Pakistan.%20The%20complete%20domination%20of%20skies%20in%20the%20eastern%20theatre%20played%20a%20decisive%20role%20in%20forcing%2093%2C000%20troops%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAerial%20Supremacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20posted%20a%20series%20of%20threads%20about%20its%20history%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20highlighting%20the%20crucial%20role%20played%20in%20a%20war%20that%20changed%20the%20world%20map.%20Operations%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20forced%20Lt%20General%20AAK%20Niazi-led%20Pakistani%20forces%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2014%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20bombed%20the%20Governor%20House%20in%20Dhaka%20when%20a%20meeting%20was%20ongoing%20in%20the%20building.%20The%20air%20strike%20had%20such%20a%20demoralizing%20effect%20that%20the%20East%20Pakistan%20government%20resigned%20on%20the%20spot.%20This%20was%20the%20last%20straw%20on%20the%20camel's%20back%20and%20Niazi%20chose%20peace%20over%20more%20fighting.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20Lt%20Gen%20Niazi%20reached%20Indian%20Army%20chief%20General%20Sam%20Manekshaw%2C%20seeking%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Manekshaw%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20expect%20you%20to%20issue%20orders%20to%20all%20forces%20under%20your%20command%20in%20Bangladesh%20to%20ceasefire%20immediately%20and%20surrender%20to%20my%20advancing%20forces.%26quot%3B%20Niazi%20had%20no%20other%20option%20and%20December%2016%20was%20set%20as%20the%20day%20of%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20put%20a%20temporary%20halt%20in%20its%20air%20operations%20till%209%3A00%20am%20on%20December%2016%2C%20this%20pause%20on%20operations%20was%20done%20on%20General%20Manekshaw's%20assurance%20to%20Lt%20Gen%20Niazi%20that%20no%20air%20operation%20would%20be%20conducted%20from%205%3A00%20pm%20on%20December%2015.%20When%20barely%20thirty%20minutes%20were%20left%20before%20the%20%26quot%3Bbombing%20pause%26quot%3B%20expired%20Lt%20Gen%20Niazi%20sought%20an%20extension%20till%203%20pm%20and%20said%20he%20was%20going%20ahead%20with%20the%20surrender%20and%20due%20to%20communication%20and%20isolation%20of%20troops%2C%20requested%20the%20truce%20to%20be%20extended%20by%20six%20hours.%20This%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20demoralizing%20effect%20IAF%20operations%20had%20in%20East%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20temporary%20halt%20in%20air%20operations%20till%200900%20hrs%