0all%2C%20it%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%C2%A0coronavirus%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bremen%20midfielder%20Leonardo%20Bittencourt%20said%20of%20the%20fans%E2%80%99%20silence%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20games%20played%20with%20no%20paying%20spectators%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DFL%20have%20said%20they%20are%20aiming%20to%20boost%20its%20business%20model%20and%20international%20marketing%20with%20the%20income%20they%20will%20receive%20from%20the%20strategic%20partner%2C%20who%20will%20have%20no%20saying%20in%20sporting%20matters%20such%20as%20fixtures%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbundesliga-fans-protest-against-private-equity-investors%2Fa-67744834%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702803241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17142248%2FGBZ8c1raEAAZip4.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbundesliga-fans-protest-against-private-equity-investors%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20by%20the%20German%20Football%20League%20to%20allow%20a%20private%20equity%20investor%20for%20the%20next%20two%20decades%20has%20sparked%20backlash%20from%20fans.%20In%20one%20incident%2C%20Hansa%20Rostock%20fans%20threw%20pyrotechnics%2C%20injuring%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbundesliga-fans-protest-against-private-equity-investors%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Small%20plane%20crashes%20into%20power%20lines%20in%20Oregon%20and%20kills%203%2C%20police%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702803164000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106062105%2Cimgsize-13220.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsmall-plane-crashes