29CD%2Fproduction%2F_132073267_gettyimages-1852673733.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67740976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stonemasons%20died%20while%20carrying%20out%20repairs%20on%20the%20Unesco%20World%20Heritage%20site%20in%20Tunisia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67740976%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67740976.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67740976.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice's%20Big%20Remarks%20On%20Gender%20Pay%20Gap%20In%20India%2C%20Homemakers'%20Rights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20law%20needs%20to%20address%20gender%20inequality%20that%20persists%20within%20households%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20privacy%20cannot%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcloak%20for%20infringement%20of%20rights%26quot%3B.%C2%A0The%20Chief%20Justice%20was%20speaking%20at%20a%20lecture%20at%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%20University%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20India's%2019th%20Chief%20Justice%20ES%20Venkataramaiah.%20Justice%20Venkataramiah's%20daughter%2C%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%2C%20is%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20and%20in%20line%20to%20become%20India's%20first%20woman%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%20memorial%20lecture%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20the%20purpose%20of%20law%20has%20to%20be%20expanded%20to%20safeguard%20participants%20in%20both%20public%20and%20private%20spaces.%20He%20then%20said%20he%20would%20be%20looking%20at%20gender%20discrimination%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20public%20and%20private%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20he%20said%2C%20provides%20that%20when%20two%20or%20more%20persons%20disturb%20public%20peace%20by%20getting%20into%20a%20brawl%2C%20they%20are%20said%20to%20commit%20an%20offence.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20punishable%20only%20if%20it%20is%20a%20public%20place%20and%20not%20otherwise.%20Thus%2C%20the%20thrust%20of%20the%20law%20is%20not%20only%20the%20inherent%20merit%20or%20demerit%20of%20brawls%2C%20but%20where%20it%20is%20taking%20place.%20A%20holistic%2C%20constitutionally%20governed%20society%20must%20be%20willing%20to%20look%20beyond%20this%20binary%20of%20public%20and%20private%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dichotomy%20of%20what%20is%20public%20and%20private%20has%20formed%20the%20basis%20of%20feminist%20and%20economic%20critique%20of%20our%20laws%20for%20several%20years%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20freedom%20of%20expression%20to%20truly%20exist%2C%20it%20has%20to%20exist%20in%20both%20these%20spaces%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20hierarchy%20persists%20in%20the%20private%20space%20and%20the%20law%20looks%20in%20the%20other%20way%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20household%2C%20we%20would%20be%20failing%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20equal%20protection%20of%20the%20law%20and%20qualifying%20it%20with%20a%20caveat%20based%20on%20the%20location%20of%20wrongdoing.%20This%20will%20be%20a%20diluted%20understanding%20of%20what%20privacy%20entails.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20cloak%20for%20infringement%20of%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20a%20household%20as%20a%20private%20space%20is%20a%20site%20of%20economic%20activity%20for%20a%20homemaker%20who%20is%20not%20remunerated%20for%20her%20service.%20%26quot%3BSimilarly%20in%20public%20places%2C%20women%20are%20confined%20to%20distinctive%20service%20oriented%20and%20often%20sexualised%20occupations%20and%20thus%20both%20sides%20have%20rights%20and%20their%20infringement.%20However%2C%20if%20law%20chooses%20it%20will%20interfere%20only%20in%20(the)%20latter%2C%20that%20is%20public%20space%2C%20then%20that%20law%20will%20be%20unjust%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20sense%20of%20justice%20evolves%20when%20we%20are%20ready%20and%20willing%20to%20open%20our%20minds%20beyond%20the%20assumption%20that%20society%20has%20taught%20us%20to%20hold.%20It%20is%20only%20when%20we%20have%20an%20open%20mind%20are%20we%20likely%20to%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20deviate%20from%20these%20base%20assumptions%20to%20curate%20our%20own%20sense%20of%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20technology%20has%20ended%20spatial%20constraints%20and%20laws%20must%C2%A0%26quot%3Bidentify%20the%20oppressed%20and%20oppressor%2C%20regardless%20of%20where%20they%20are%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20home%20is%20a%20site%20of%20economic%20employment%20for%20a%20house%20help%2C%20does%20the%20law%20give%20the%20same%20benefits%20to%20the%20person%20as%20a%20corporate%20employee%2C%20he%20asked%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20aged%20notion%20that%20what%20men%20do%20is%20public%2C%20and%20what%20women%20do%20is%20private%20has%20no%20application%20in%20society%20governed%20by%20constitutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20gender%20pay%20gap%20in%20India%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20issue%20is%20particularly%20pronounced%20for%20Indian%20women%2C%20especially%20those%20belonging%20to%20a%20marginalised%20community.%20Despite%20their%20significant%20contributions%20to%20various%20professional%20spheres%2C%20women%20continue%20to%20face%20disparity%20in%20remunerations%20compared%20to%20their%20male%20counterparts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702801860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fp5lblf5_justice-dy-chandrachud_625x300_17_December_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachuds-big-remarks-on-gender-pay-gap-in-india-homemakers-rights-4689976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Explaining%20why%20law%20needs%20to%20address%20gender%20inequality%20that%20persists%20within%20households%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20privacy%20cannot%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcloak%20for%20infringement%20of%20rights%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachuds-big-remarks-on-gender-pay-gap-in-india-homemakers-rights-4689976%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachuds-big-remarks-on-gender-pay-gap-in-india-homemakers-rights-4689976%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachuds-big-remarks-on-gender-pay-gap-in-india-homemakers-rights-4689976%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Phantasm%20of%20Triumphalism%20on%20Kashmir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17121316%2Fimad-clicks-Dg6tMlfSOQ4-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-kashmir-article-370-verdict%5C%22%3Eruling%20on%20Article%20370%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20given%20a%20seal%20of%20finality%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20and%20relegated%20the%20subject%20to%20a%20matter%20of%20academic%20debates.%20The%20questions%20of%20whether%20this%20was%20done%20to%20suit%20the%20iron-fisted%20majoritarian%20policies%20of%20the%20government%2C%20and%20whether%20legal%20and%20historic%20facts%20were%20considered%20or%20skirted%2C%20will%20soon%20be%20reduced%20to%20the%20footnotes%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20realities%20will%20be%20forgotten.%20What%20will%20remain%20is%20the%20alteration%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20which%20now%20hangs%20by%20flimsy%20excuses%20and%20not%20cemented%20by%20constitutionality.%20What%20also%20remains%20is%20the%20overwhelming%20celebration%20of%20a%20brute%20majority%20that%20sledgehammers%20the%20voice%20and%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20who%20have%20been%20impacted%20by%20this%20decision%2C%20who%20feel%20already%20betrayed%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20humiliated%20in%20the%20times%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20celebratory%20note%20is%20driven%20through%20words%20like%20%E2%80%9Cintegration%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cunity%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cend%20to%20terrorism%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cprogress%E2%80%9D.%20Distortions%20about%20Article%20370%20and%20what%20it%20signified%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20invoked%2C%20pedalled%20and%20amplified%20to%20reinforce%20a%20sense%20of%20triumphalism%20or%20to%20turn%20them%20into%20pivots%20of%20some%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20Mexican%20pi%C3%B1ata%20signifying%20the%20seven%20deadly%20sins%2C%20and%20beating%20it%20is%20being%20deemed%20an%20act%20of%20faith%20by%20the%20blindfolded%2C%20who%20imagine%20and%20re-imagine%20the%20cardinal%20sins%20of%20this%20constitutional%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20serve%20little%20purpose%20to%20dispel%20some%20of%20the%20myths%20around%20Article%20370%2C%20now%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20apex%20court%20appears%20have%20given%20its%20legal%20sanctity%20to%20some%20of%20them.%20Yet%2C%20truth%20must%20be%20told%20even%20long%20after%20the%20damage%20has%20been%20done.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20deconstruct%20two%20main%20myths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMyth%201%3A%20Article%20370%20encouraged%20terrorism%2C%20hindered%20security%20interests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20myth%20is%20based%20on%20an%20erroneous%20understanding%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20history%20and%20the%20legality%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20This%20would%20suggest%20that%20separatism%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20draws%20its%20strength%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20terrorists%20can%20operate%20only%20while%20weaponising%20these%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20which%20relied%20on%20this%20distortion%20and%20stated%20that%20Article%20370%20was%20inserted%20due%20to%20a%20war-like%20situation%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20war%20was%20long%20over%20when%20Article%20370%20was%20ratified%20unanimously%20and%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20adopted%20in%201949.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%20was%20in%20existence%20for%20another%20four%20decades%20before%20insurgency%20started%20in%20Kashmir.%20The%20insurgency%20was%20decimated%20and%20reduced%20from%20thousands%20of%20armed%20guerillas%20to%20just%20over%20a%20hundred%20by%202010%2C%20and%20then%20gradually%20re-energised.%20Before%20Article%20370%20was%20demolished%20in%202019%2C%20there%20were%20about%20200-250%20militants%20operating%20in%20Kashmir.%20The%20numbers%20remain%20static%20despite%20Article%20370%20being%20bulldozed.%20In%20fact%2C%20militancy%20related%20incidents%20have%20spilled%20over%20to%20Rajouri-Poonch%20and%20the%20Chenab%20Valley%20of%20Jammu%20region%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nehru%20and%20Kashmir%3A%20After%20SC's%20Article%20370%20Order%2C%20BJP%20Attempts%C2%A0to%20Distort%20History%20Again%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnehru-kashmir-article-370-rss-bjp-distort-history%5C%22%3ENehru%20and%20Kashmir%3A%20After%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Article%20370%20Order%2C%20BJP%20Attempts%C2%A0to%20Distort%20History%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20ceasefire%20has%20been%20maintained%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20was%20also%20in%20place%20between%202003%20and%202013%20enabling%20the%20opening%20of%20trade%20and%20bus%20routes%20between%20the%20two%20parts%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20separated%20by%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%2C%20since%202019%20the%20eastern%20borders%20in%20Ladakh%20have%20witnessed%20unusual%20and%20increased%20hostility%2C%20allowing%20China%20to%20guzzle%20up%20vast%20chunks%20of%20Indian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%20is%20not%20the%20cause%20of%20militancy%20or%20hostilities%20on%20the%20borders.%20To%20the%20contrary%2C%20whittling%20away%20of%20autonomy%20granted%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20under%20Article%20370%20was%20a%20contributing%20factor%20in%20provoking%20the%201989%20insurgency%20or%20the%20recent%20Chinese%20incursions.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMyth%202%3A%20Article%20370%20was%20an%20obstacle%20to%20the%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%20was%20an%20affirmation%20of%20the%20special%20circumstances%20in%20which%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20acceded%20to%20India%20and%20of%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20Indian%20Union%20to%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Contrary%20to%20popular%20perception%2C%20it%20did%20not%20weaken%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20state%3B%20it%20strengthened%20it%20as%20it%20provided%20the%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20link%20to%20a%20state%20that%20was%20originally%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20dominion%20when%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20were%20partitioned%20in%20August%201947.%20It%20was%20thus%20an%20affirmation%20of%20the%20integration%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20India%20on%20the%20conditions%20of%20its%20special%20status%20within%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20the%20basis%20of%20which%20was%20the%20Instrument%20of%20Accession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20affirmation%20further%20got%20a%20layer%20of%20legal%20and%20democratic%20sanctity%20when%20the%20Constitution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20framed%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Constituent%20Assembly%20and%20Article%20370%20was%20its%20foundational%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%201956%2C%20starts%20with%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20having%20solemnly%20resolved%E2%80%A6to%20further%20define%20the%20existing%20relationship%20of%20the%20State%20with%20the%20Union%20of%20India%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%203%20of%20the%20Constitution%20lays%20down%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20and%20shall%20be%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%20Section%205%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20executive%20and%20legislative%20power%20of%20the%20State%20extends%20to%20all%20matters%20except%20those%20with%20respect%20to%20which%20Parliament%20has%20power%20to%20make%20laws%20for%20the%20State%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20147%20prohibited%20any%20amendments%20to%20Section%203%2C%20further%20making%20the%20provision%20absolute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20There%20Is%20Silence%20in%20Kashmir%20Over%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20Verdict%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-there-is-silence-in-kashmir-over-the-supreme-courts-verdict%5C%22%3EWhy%20There%20Is%20Silence%20in%20Kashmir%20Over%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20integration%20of%20the%20state%20was%20thus%20affirmed%20by%20an%20elected%20and%20democratically%20representative%20body%2C%20that%20supersedes%20all%20other%20previous%20proclamations%2C%20including%20the%20one%20by%20the%20royal%20heir%20apparent%20Yuvraj%20Karan%20Singh%20(which%20the%20court%20relied%20on).%20This%20meant%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20had%20ratified%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20temporary%20only%20till%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Constituent%20Assembly%20could%20take%20a%20final%20decision%2C%20and%20chose%20to%20be%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Union%20while%20maintaining%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20own%20federal%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20other%20arrangement%20between%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20that%20torpedoes%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20will%20through%20backdoor%20legislations%20endorsed%20by%20the%20court%2C%20may%20be%20technically%20legitimate%20but%20defies%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20democracy%20which%20place%20people%20at%20the%20core%20of%20every%20decision-making%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20new%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20arrangement%20of%20integration%20means%20that%20the%20territory%20has%20been%20integrated%20but%20the%20people%20have%20been%20weaned%20away.%20History%20has%20been%20instructive%20that%20the%20brutal%20attempts%20to%20manipulate%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20politics%20and%20society%20have%20not%20helped%20integrate%20the%20people%20but%20caused%20more%20alienation%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20humiliation%20and%20betrayal.%20With%20this%20final%20betrayal%20%E2%80%93%20signalling%20the%20lack%20of%20any%20hope%20of%20winning%20back%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20people%20%E2%80%93%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20new%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%20is%20being%20built%20over%20the%20old%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%20where%20progress%20and%20development%20will%20be%20measured%20by%20the%20profits%20reaped%20by%20corporates%2C%20big%20businessmen%20with%20deep%20pockets%20and%20mining%20mafia%20from%20outside%20the%20state%2C%20while%20the%20permanent%20residents%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20squabble%20for%20jobs%2C%20business%20ventures%2C%20land%2C%20basic%20essentials%20like%20electricity%20and%20water%20and%20bear%20the%20colossal%20consequences%20of%20the%20ecological%20vandalism%20that%20comes%20with%20reckless%20planning%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%20where%20selfie-taking%20tourists%20and%20tourism%20is%20deemed%20to%20be%20the%20sole%20index%20of%20the%20happiness%20and%20robustness%20of%20the%20state%2C%20even%20as%20local%20markets%20and%20roads%20outside%20the%20tourist%20areas%20begin%20to%20look%20like%20the%20ruins%20of%20some%20ancient%20site.%20The%20houses%20and%20business%20establishments%20will%20be%20bulldozed%20or%20attached%20on%20the%20most%20frivolous%20pretexts%20and%20JCBs%20will%20run%20over%20carts%20of%20vendors%20in%20beautification%20drives.%20In%20this%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%2C%20people%20will%20also%20lose%20jobs%20and%20be%20arrested%20for%20daring%20to%20speak%20or%20having%20dared%20to%20speak%20some%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20the%20youth%20will%20be%20detained%20for%20democratically%20protesting%20over%20issues%20of%20unemployment%20and%20tribal%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETriumphalism%20over%20what%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Indians%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20those%20who%20subscribe%20to%20majoritarian%20sentiments%20but%20even%20some%20of%20the%20so-called%20liberals%20%E2%80%93%20however%2C%20will%20rejoice%20mindless%20of%20the%20sense%20of%20loss%20and%20betrayal%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(Ladakh%20included).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20rejoicing%20a%20%E2%80%98new%20era%20of%20peace%3F%20Terrorism%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20threat.%20History%20shows%20a%20directly%20proportional%20relationship%20between%20deepening%20trust%20deficit%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20insurgency.%20The%20sense%20of%20betrayal%20and%20lack%20of%20faith%20in%20Indian%20democracy%20has%20reached%20a%20new%20low%20%E2%80%93%20to%20a%20point%20from%20where%20it%20can%20go%20no%20further.%20Could%20this%20betrayal%20sow%20the%20seeds%20of%20another%20wave%20of%20virulent%20resistance%2C%20if%20not%20armed%20terrorism%3F%20It%20may%20not%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20if%2C%20but%20when.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20rejoicing%20the%20%E2%80%98calm%20and%20silence%E2%80%99%3F%20Nobody%20criticises%20the%20Indian%20government.%20No%20one%20talks%20about%20right%20to%20self-determination.%20Stone%20pelting%20has%20gone%20but%20that%20has%20been%20controlled%20under%20excessive%20repression%20and%20military%20jackboots.%20Beyond%20a%20point%2C%20this%20repression%20does%20not%20work.%20If%20and%20when%20there%20is%20a%20backfire%20effect%2C%20what%20would%20that%20look%20like%3F%20What%20would%20be%20the%20terms%20on%20which%20anyone%20smitten%20by%20a%20history%20of%20betrayals%20would%20want%20to%20negotiate%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Last%20Pillar%20of%20Indian%20Democracy%20Has%20Fallen%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-last-pillar-of-indian-democracy-has-fallen%5C%22%3EThe%20Last%20Pillar%20of%20Indian%20Democracy%20Has%20Fallen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20rejoicing%20the%20betrayal%20of%20the%20people%20who%20decided%20to%20be%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20country%20seven%20decades%20ago%3F%20At%20least%20some%20of%20them%20would%20be%20rejoicing%20how%20the%20demography%20of%20the%20only%20Muslim-majority%20state%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98democratic%2C%20secular%20India%E2%80%99%20can%20now%20be%20changed.%20How%20does%20that%20make%20Indian%20democracy%20look%3F%20What%20does%20it%20do%20it%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20standing%3F%20Perhaps%20those%20who%20take%20pleasure%20in%20vilifying%20Muslims%20and%20wish%20to%20create%20a%20country%20where%20Muslims%20are%20reduced%20to%20second-rate%20citizens%20may%20also%20take%20pride%20in%20what%20they%20rejoice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20rejoicing%20the%20butchery%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20asymmetric%20federalism%3F%20How%20will%20a%20court%20verdict%20that%20sets%20a%20precedent%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20and%20motives%20cannot%20be%20challenged%20or%20deemed%20to%20be%20ill-intentioned%20impact%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20and%20its%20federalism%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20at%20all%20there%20is%20a%20realisation%20of%20the%20monumental%20blunders%20made%20in%20watering%20down%20Article%20370%20and%20robbing%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20of%20its%20autonomy%2C%20when%20it%20comes%2C%20much%20damage%20would%20have%20been%20done%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20in%20the%20region%20but%20also%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20some%20of%20it%20may%20be%20reparable%2C%20any%20road%20for%20a%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20particularly%20its%20Muslim%20population%2C%20may%20be%20next%20to%20impossible.%20All%20bridges%20have%20been%20deliberately%20demolished.%20For%20now%2C%20it%20seems%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnuradha%20Bashin%20is%20Executive%20Editor%20of%20Kashmir%20Times%2C%20Senior%20JSK%20Journalism%20Fellow%20and%20author%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0A%20Dismantled%20State%3A%20Untold%20Story%20of%20Kashmir%20After%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702801804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17121316%2Fimad-clicks-Dg6tMlfSOQ4-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-phantasm-of-triumphalism-on-kashmir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20may%20serve%20little%20purpose%20to%20dispel%20some%20of%20the%20myths%20around%20Article%20370%2C%20now%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20apex%20court%20appears%20have%20given%20its%20legal%20sanctity%20to%20some%20of%20them.%20Yet%2C%20truth%20mus