gangsters%2C%20but%20the%20details%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20eighth%20encounter%20reported%20in%20the%20last%2011%20days%20in%20Punjab%2C%20notably%20after%20an%20open%20warning%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20that%20the%20police%20will%20retaliate%20if%20they%20come%20under%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20encounters%20were%20reported%20yesterday%20from%20Mohali%20and%20Patiala%2C%20and%20two%20car%20thieves%20and%20a%20murder%20accused%20were%20arrested.%20All%20three%20sustained%20injuries%20in%20firing%20in%20both%20the%20incidents%2C%20police%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702800420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ft2975sk_punjab-encounter-moga_625x300_17_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-encounter-in-punjab-after-gangsters-fire-at-cops-chasing-them-4689882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20crackdown%20on%20gangsters%20in%20Punjab%20continued%20on%20Sunday%20with%20another%20encounter%20in%20Moga%20district%20early%20this%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-encounter-in-punjab-after-gangsters-fire-at-cops-chasing-them-4689882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-encounter-in-punjab-after-gangsters-fire-at-cops-chasing-them-4689882%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanother-encounter-in-punjab-after-gangsters-fire-at-cops-chasing-them-4689882%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBlue%20Origin%20Needs%20Me%26quot%3B%3A%20Jeff%20Bezos%20On%20Stepping%20Down%20As%20Amazon%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJeff%20Bezos%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20e-commerce%20giant%20Amazon%2C%20has%20shared%20the%20reason%20behind%20his%20decision%20to%20step%20down%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20company%20two%20years%20ago.%20The%20drastic%20step%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20the%20world%2C%20and%20now%20Mr%20Bezos%20has%20cited%20his%20motivations%20for%20the%20same%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDcWqzZ3I2cY%5C%22%3Eepisode%20of%20the%20Lex%20Fridman%20Podcast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bezos%20said%20it%20is%20his%20commitment%20to%20his%20space%20exploration%20venture%20Blue%20Origin%20that%20served%20as%20the%20primary%20contributor%20to%20his%20retirement%20decision.%20Explaining%20the%20decision%20to%20move%20away%20from%20the%20CEO%20role%20of%20the%20company%20he%20founded%20in%201994%2C%20the%20billionaire%20said%20that%20his%20space%20venture%20needed%20to%20grow%20at%20a%20faster%20pace%20and%20this%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20if%20it%20had%20to%20manage%20both%20Blue%20Origin%20and%20Amazon%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CBlue%20Origin%20needs%20to%20be%20much%20faster.%20And%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20I%20left%20my%20role%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20Amazon%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20wanted%20to%20come%20in%20and%20Blue%20Origin%20needs%20me%20right%20now'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Not%20providing%20full%20attention%20to%20Amazon%20would%20then%20be%20unfair%20to%20its%20stakeholders%2C%20Mr%20Bezos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20so%2C%20I%20had%20always%20%E2%80%A6%20When%20I%20was%20the%20CEO%20of%20Amazon%2C%20my%20point%20of%20view%20on%20this%20is%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20I'm%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20publicly%20traded%20company%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20get%20my%20full%20attention.'%20And%20it's%20just%20how%20I%20think%20about%20things.%20It%20was%20very%20important%20to%20me.%20I%20felt%20I%20had%20an%20obligation%20to%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20at%20Amazon%20to%20do%20that.%20And%20so%20having%20turned%20the%20CEO%2C%20I'm%20still%20the%20executive%20chair%20there%2C%20b