nonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Femir-sheikh-nawaf-laid-to-rest-in-kuwait%2Farticleshow%2F106061092.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Femir-sheikh-nawaf-laid-to-rest-in-kuwait%2Famp_articleshow%2F106061092.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Femir-sheikh-nawaf-laid-to-rest-in-kuwait%2Famp_articleshow%2F106061092.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Special%20Team%20To%20Probe%20Case%20Of%20Woman%20Hit%20By%20Bureaucrat's%20Son%20With%20Car%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20charges%20of%20a%20woman%20that%20her%20boyfriend%20-%20a%20senior%20bureaucrat's%20son%20-%20allegedly%20knocked%20her%20down%20with%20his%20car%20after%20a%20fight%20in%20Thane%20city%20near%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20under%20sections%20related%20to%20voluntarily%20causing%20hurt%20and%20rash%20driving%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Ashwajit%20Gaikwad%2C%20on%20the%20charges%20by%20Priya%20Singh%2C%2026%2C%20who%20is%20now%20hospitalised%2C%20said%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20thorough%20investigation%2C%20an%20SIT%20has%20been%20formed%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police%20Zone%205%20Amar%20Singh%20Jadhav%2C%20and%20it%20is%20probing%20into%20all%20angles%20of%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Thane%20police%20commissioner%20Jai%20Jeet%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20cops%20are%20recording%20statements%20of%20witnesses%20and%20collecting%20forensic%20evidence.%20More%20charges%20will%20be%20added%20after%20more%20facts%20emerge%20during%20the%20probe%2C%20added%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwajit%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Anil%20Gaikwad%2C%20the%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Road%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singh%20had%20alleged%20she%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Ashwajit%20for%20four-and-a-half%20years%20and%20he%20had%20hidden%20his%20marriage%20from%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20early%20morning%20on%20December%2011%20when%20Ms%20Singh%20had%20gone%20to%20meet%20Ashwajit%20at%20a%20function.%20When%20she%20reached%20there%2C%20she%20saw%20him%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20this%20led%20to%20an%20argument.%20She%20alleged%20that%20when%20she%20reached%20into%20Ashwajit's%20car%20to%20collect%20her%20belongings%2C%20he%20asked%20his%20driver%20to%20run%20her%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20fell%20down%20in%20the%20impact%20and%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%2C%20police%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20has%20put%20out%20several%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20over%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20terrified.%20I'm%20very%20scared%20for%20my%20family%20and%20myself.%20I%20don't%20feel%20safe.%20I%20have%20lost%20all%20faith%20in%20humanity.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20my%20life%20is%20ever%20going%20to%20be%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20one%20of%20her%20Instagram%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702799280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Foiqeasg8_priya-singh-ashwajit-gaikwad_625x300_16_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-horror-special-team-to-probe-womans-case-after-being-run-over-by-bureaucrats-son-4689914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20charges%20of%20a%20woman%20that%20her%20boyfriend%20-%20a%20senior%20bureaucrat's%20son%20-%20allegedly%20knocked%20her%20down%20with%20his%20car%20after%20a%20fight%20in%20Thane%20city%20near%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-horror-special-team-to-probe-womans-case-after-