n%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-anniversary-slogan-dictatorship%5C%22%3Eserious%20breach%20of%20security%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20was.%20The%20ruling%20dispensation%20reacted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-the-govts-response-to-parliament-security-breach-was-a-bundle-of-contradictions%5C%22%3Etreating%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20as%20a%20serious%20conspiracy%2C%20maybe%20not%20entirely%20spontaneous%2C%20but%20orchestrated%20by%20unseen%20%E2%80%98enemies%20of%20the%20State%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMediapersons%20swiftly%20began%20squabbling%20over%20a%20canister%20that%20the%20attackers%20had%20allegedly%20used%20to%20release%20yellow%20smoke.%20Amit%20Malviya%2C%20in-charge%20of%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20National%20Information%20and%20Technology%20Department%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Fjairam-ramesh-lavanya-ballal-jain-amit-malviya-bjp-congress-opposition-parliament-security-breach-11702533686419.html%5C%22%3Edubbed%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20security%20breaches%20accused%20Neelam%20Verma%20as%20a%20mere%20%E2%80%98Andolanjeevi%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20term%20popularised%20by%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20246px)%2085vw%2C%20246px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22246%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20the%20visuals.%20Two%20young%20men%20suddenly%20jump%20into%20the%20new%20Parliament%20while%20it%20was%20in%20session%2C%20yelling%20and%20waving%20canisters%20that%20released%20a%20noxious%20yellow%20gas%2C%20leap%20across%20seats%20and%20tables.%20The%20suddenness%20took%20everyone%20by%20surprise%2C%20and%20most%20of%20them%20chose%20to%20rush%20out%2C%20while%20a%20few%20stood%20on%20the%20sidelines%20with%20mouths%20agape%20before%20pouncing%20on%20the%20culprits.%20Outside%2C%20Neelam%20Azad%20(37)%2C%20a%20woman%20protester%2C%20was%20dragged%20away%20while%20shouting%20slogans%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fyouth-unemployment-rate-in-india-was-higher-than-its-neighbours-in-2022-world-bank-report%5C%22%3Eyouth%20unemployment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20haunted%20them.%20The%20term%20%E2%80%98Andolanjeevi%E2%80%99%20thus%20gained%20young%20faces%20contorted%20with%20rage%20that%20should%20now%20frighten%20more%20citizens%2C%20anchors%2C%20reporters%2C%20and%20certainly%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20media%20handlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20is%20well-armed%20to%20handle%20such%20rage.%20Of%20late%20the%20ambit%20of%20old%20criminal%20laws%20the%20British%20used%20to%20punish%20revolutionaries%20is%20being%20expanded%20and%20used%20liberally.%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20rebellion%20surfaces%20first%20among%20the%20young%20and%20can%20soon%20become%20a%20wave%20if%20times%20are%20ripe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20market%20has%20many%20flaws%2C%20the%20new%20social%20media%20it%20has%20launched%20has%20also%20made%20democratic%20functioning%20transparent.%20Young%20people%20are%20avid%20observers%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20their%20leaders%2C%20who%20are%20carefully%20and%20expensively%20%E2%80%98relabelled%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98repackaged%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20whose%20narratives%20are%20%E2%80%98reset%E2%80%99%20by%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20are%20no%20longer%20joyous%20occasions%20celebrating%20democratic%20freedoms.%20They%20are%20wars%20fought%20in%20cyberspace.%20The%20voters%20here%20are%20data.%20The%20faceless%20vote%20banks%20are%20wooed%20in%20rallies%20and%20on%20TV%20with%20%C2%A0%E2%80%98presentations%E2%80%99%20and%20panel%20discussions%20on%20prime%20time%20TV.%20The%20upstart%20anchors%2C%20with%20carefully%20styled%20hair%2C%20no%20longer%20talk%20of%20national%20priorities%2C%20but%20%E2%80%98brand%20identity%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98core%20values%E2%80%99%2C%20state%20models%2C%20double-engines.%20Even%20the%20group%20ads%20boast%20not%20of%20viewers%20but%20of%20channels%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98market%20share%E2%80%99.%20Systems%20turn%20away%20again%20and%20again%20from%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%3A%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20we%20are%20sold%20old%20wine%20in%20new%20bottles%20and%20mutton%20parading%20as%20lamb%2C%20talking%20about%20India%20as%20a%20young%20nation%2C%20youthful%20dreams%2C%20and%20restoring%20the%20lost%20glory%20of%20the%20wonder%20that%20was%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20nation%20hastily%20bulldozes%20these%20angry%20young%20voices%2C%20it%20must%20take%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20face%20the%20real-time%20issues%20that%20will%20remain%20unresolved%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20margin%20political%20parties%20may%20win.%20The%20basic%20flaw%20must%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20get%20buried%20under%20ritual%20and%20spectacle.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20it%20lies%20in%20a%20poor%20security%20set%20up%20for%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%20The%20building%20was%20inaugurated%20not%20too%20long%20ago%20in%20a%20ritualistic%20ceremony%2C%20with%20a%20horde%20of%20portly%20Sadhus%20carrying%20a%20gold%20mace%2C%20The%20Holy%20Sengol%20%E2%80%93%20an%20ancient%20symbol%20of%20divine%20authority%20%E2%80%93%20and%20planting%20it%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20Democracy%20amid%20Vedic%20chants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20media%20buzz%20was%20good%20Vastu%2C%20holy%20Mantras%20and%20ancient%20rituals%20that%20protect%20our%20culture%20and%20democracy.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20whiff%20of%20the%20objective%20conditions%20many%20of%20our%20youngsters%20are%20growing%20in.%20Some%20will%20view%20this%20question%20as%20cynical.%20After%20all%2C%20they%20ask%2C%20such%20conditions%20exist%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20but%20a%20blatant%20attack%20within%20the%20Parliament%20building%20by%20half%20a%20dozen%20rank%20amateurs%20with%20personal%20grievances%20against%20the%20system%2C%20does%20not%20erupt%20there.%20Why%20did%20it%20happen%20here%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%20so%20suddenly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-yellow-smoke-signals-tell-us-about-the-mother-of-democracy%5C%22%3EWhat%20Yellow%20Smoke%20Signals%20Tell%20Us%20About%20the%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20sudden%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20reports.%20The%20educated%20but%20jobless%20individuals%20had%20met%20briefly%20in%20Mysuru%20over%20a%20year%20ago.%20Since%20then%2C%20they%20kept%20in%20touch%20on%20Facebook%20and%20recently%20reunited%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20the%20Maximum%20City%20of%20the%20north%2C%20to%20shape%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20draw%20attention%20to%20their%20plight.%20Facebook%20is%20a%20bubble%20created%20for%20their%20kind%20by%20a%20Harvard%20sophomore%20to%20whom%20%E2%80%98connectivity%20among%20the%20young%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20Holy%20Grail.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Fan%20Club%20page%2C%20built%20around%20the%20celebrated%20rebel%20against%20British%20colonialism%20who%20had%20also%20hurled%20a%20dummy%20bomb%20at%20the%20highest%20authority%2C%20became%20the%20catalyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENet%20is%20where%20our%20youngsters%20live%2024%C3%977.%20And%20everything%20shrinks%20on%20Facebook%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20mini%20India%20for%20the%20young%2C%20with%20time%20on%20their%20hands%20that%20they%20can%20roam%20freely%20to%20meet%20like-minded%20people.%20Here%20is%20where%20a%20Neelam%20Azad%2C%20the%20jobless%20daughter%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehalwai%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Jind%20who%20has%20an%20M.Ed%20degree%2C%20has%20passed%20the%20NET%2C%20HTET%2C%20CTET%20exams%20and%20still%20failed%20to%20get%20a%20job%2C%20could%20meet%20another%20disgruntled%2026-year-old%20Sagar%20Sharma%2C%20son%20of%20a%20carpenter%2C%20who%20had%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%20for%20lack%20of%20money%20and%20drive%20an%20auto%20rickshaw%20in%20Lucknow%20for%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20met%20a%20jobless%20engineer%2C%20Manoranjan%20(34)%20from%20Mysuru%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20farmer%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%20(25)%2C%20a%20Dalit%20from%20Latur%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20who%20failed%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20army%20and%20was%20deemed%20too%20old%20for%20becoming%20an%20Agniveer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Facebook%2C%20Vishal%20Sharma%20and%20Lalit%20Jha%20promised%20to%20provide%20board%20and%20lodging%20to%20their%20out%20of%20town%20online%20friends.%20Thus%2C%20a%20Wild%20West%20of%20Facebook%20became%20home%20for%20the%20revolutionary%20fantasies%20of%20lost%2C%20frustrated%2C%20and%20angry%20souls.%20No%20wonder%20there%20is%20a%20haphazard%20and%20accidental%20quality%20to%20their%20attack.%20The%20younger%20ones%2C%20Amol%20and%20Sagar%2C%20entered%20the%20Parliament%2C%20courtesy%20passes%20provided%20by%20the%20staff%20of%20an%20unsuspecting%20MP%2C%20and%20created%20terror%20within%2C%20while%20the%20older%20ones%2C%20Neelam%20and%20Manoranjan%2C%20raised%20slogans%20and%20waved%20spray%20cans%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20bystanders%20were%20petrified%20and%20revolted%2C%20the%20media%20vultures%20entered%2C%20fighting%20over%20a%20can%20of%20tear%20gas.%20Rich%20Black%20humour%20there%2C%20but%20also%20so%20much%20unspoken%20pain!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20evening%2C%20the%20general%20reaction%20had%20subsided%20as%20authorities%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Godi%E2%80%99%20media%20went%20into%20overdrive%20trying%20to%20find%20links%20with%20all%20deemed%20subversives%3A%20Maoists%2C%20Naxals%2C%20and%20the%20Opposition%20looking%20to%20draw%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20moment%20when%20a%20nascent%20movement%20limited%20to%20some%20half%20a%20dozen%20men%20and%20women%20butted%20headlong%20in%20a%20structure%20they%20felt%20no%20longer%20cared%20for%20them.%20Like%20children%20throwing%20tantrums%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20destroy%20and%20de%20sanctify%20whatever%20they%20could%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20their%20anger%3A%20chairs%2C%20tables%2C%20papers%2C%20files%2C%20a%20mic%20here%20and%20a%20bag%20there.%20But%20these%20acts%20were%20impulsive%20and%20short-lived%2C%20a%20poor%20theatre%2C%20if%20you%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20condemnable%20but%20puny%20revolt%20underscores%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20this%3A%20sometimes%20money%20and%20spectacles%20are%20not%20enough%20to%20sustain%20the%20grand%20illusion%3B%20hollow%20promises%20are%20no%20longer%20working.%20There%20is%20an%20Iranian%20proverb%20that%20says%3A%20Promises%20have%20value%20only%20for%20those%20that%20believe%20in%20them.%20The%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20incident%20on%20December%2013%20showed%20us%20a%20rare%20glimpse%20of%20what%20many%20did%20not%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20play%20gone%20bad%20could%2C%20if%20immediate%20remedial%20action%20is%20not%20taken%2C%20become%20a%20violent%20rapacious%20spectacle%20where%20characters%20will%20again%20invade%20the%20stage%20suddenly%2C%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702794200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14095043%2FGBN2cf7bMAANLsZ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwho-are-our-young-andolanjeevis%22%