rts%2C%20she%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20secure%20justice%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20letter%2C%20written%20in%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20pain%20and%20despair%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20addressed%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20letter%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%2015%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20sought%20a%20status%20report%20from%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20on%20the%20inquiry%20being%20conducted%20into%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20raised%20by%20the%20woman%20judge.%20The%20CJI%20is%20yet%20to%20publicly%20respond%20to%20the%20matter%20or%20issue%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20system%20of%20redressal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20one%20particular%20district%20judge%20and%20his%20associates.%20I%20was%20told%20to%20meet%20the%20district%20judge%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20civil%20judge%20wrote%20in%20her%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlthough%20she%20does%20not%20state%20specific%20instances%20or%20names%20the%20accused%2C%20her%20letter%20provides%20a%20clear%20glimpse%20of%20the%20distressing%20experience%20she%20had%20to%20go%20through%20in%20order%20to%20seek%20justice%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20abused%20verbally%20in%20open%20court%20with%20a%20misogynist%20slur%20and%20that%20she%20had%20even%20tried%20to%20kill%20herself%20through%20suicide.%20The%20judge%20reportedly%20endured%20the%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20during%20her%20earlier%20posting%20in%20another%20district%20close%20to%20the%20capital%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20to%20the%20very%20limit.%20I%20have%20