e%20to%20fund%20the%20research%20for%20the%20robot.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sudhir%20once%20sold%20his%20car%20and%20furniture%20to%20fund%20the%20research%20for%20the%20robot%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20SSI%20Innovations%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20a%20real-life%20example%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20performing%20a%20surgical%20procedure%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263534%2Fanupath-tripathi-squid-game-netflix-facts-korean-drama-abdul-ali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20South%20Korea%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%202008%2C%20a%20nurse%20accidentally%20inserted%20a%20knife%20right%20through%20the%20heart.%20When%20I%20inquired%20later%2C%20she%20explained%20that%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20accurately%20gauge%20the%20depth.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20problems%20like%20this%2C%20SSI%20Mantra%202%20provides%20a%20better%20view%20of%20the%20organs%20as%20depth%20perception%20is%20crucial%20in%20surgery%20for%20bringing%20in%20instruments%20and%20supplies%2C%20avoiding%20accidents%2C%20and%20shortening%20the%20learning%20curve.%20Since%20its%20launch%20in%202022%2C%20the%20system%20has%20already%20assisted%20doctors%20in%20performing%20500%20successful%20surgeries%20in%20India.%3C%